gomodel:SYNGO_5036  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1: immunogold labeling of TRPC1 and electron microscopy of the cerebellum showed postsynaptic and, to a lesser extend, presynaptic localization. Partial co-localization was observed for immunogold labelling for TRPC1 (5 nm) and mGluR1α /GRM1 (10 nm).\n\nBased on the known transmembrane topology of this protein, \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was selected.. Experimental description: Result sections: \"To assess the ultrastructural localization of TRPC1 we performed post-embedding immuno-electron microscopy on adult rat cerebellum (Fig. 1d).\"\n\nTRPC1 antibody (Alomone)" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_5036" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
